Governor of Delta State, Rt Hon Sheriff Oborevwori has approved the appointment of Chief Edwin Uzor and Hon Funkekeme Solomon as Special Advisers. A statement by Secretary to the State Government, Dr. Kingsley Emu disclosed that others so appointed are Rt Hon Basil Ganagana, Mr Tony Amechi, Mrs Eunice Okiemute Anirah, Chief Mrs Shemitte Bello, Mr Grftson Omatsulli and Olorogun Barr Jaro Egbo. Also appointed is Hon Frank Omare as Director General, Special Duties. The statement added that dates for their inauguration shall be announced soon